The Senator Representing Kogi West in the National Assembly, Senator Dino Melaye has accepted the Appeal court verdict which nulifies his Senatorial election. In a Statement on Friday, Dino urges his supporters to remaining law-abiding, maintaining that they will always overcome. “I just lost my election at the Appeal Court and Fresh election ordered. In all things I give God the Praise. He who started a good thing will definitely complete it. I ask my supporters to be law abiding as we shall always overcome. To God be the Glory.” He noted. The Appeal court on Friday had nulify the Kogi West Senatorial election which Dino was declared winner ordering a fresh election. Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook 